&lt;p>为了保证可读性，对原文有一些调整和改编，请放心阅读。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>——2019.3.11 &lt;/p></description></item><item><title>清凉翻译#1：IIDX与下落式音游的读谱</title><link>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/cowlevel_backup_09/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Feb 2019 20:48:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/cowlevel_backup_09/</guid><description>&lt;p>本文来自一个日基的博客：&lt;a href="https://the-safari.com">サファリドットコム&lt;/a>。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>IIDX 好弟弟折腾笔记</title><link>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/cowlevel_backup_00/</link><pubDate>Wed, 26 Dec 2018 11:54:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/cowlevel_backup_00/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;del>牛关竟然没有街机IIDX的条目&lt;/del>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>人间百曲</title><link>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/game_review_01/</link><pubDate>Wed, 30 May 2018 02:24:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/game_review_01/</guid><description>&lt;p>当时也写的很认真呢。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>For Respect！ #新手入坑指南</title><link>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/cowlevel_backup_06/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2017 20:57:25 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://shinonome-shizuka.github.io/post/cowlevel_backup_06/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>历时10.7个月，我白金了，开始向100%进发。&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>